ue; what new value do you unveil? \n\n16. In the gem of the Caribbean where sandy beaches await, what is the elevation of the island that entices travelers looking for paradise? \n\n17. Report the number of fans that can gather at the home of the football squad, showcasing their local pride and vibrant spirit.\n\n18. Finally, calculate: (clue 3 + clue 15 + clue 17) % 10. This journey ends with a single digit to carry forth.",
